data.description: 6 BR 2.5 BA Fabulous home on a cul-de-sac with extended paver driveway. The bright island kitchen is well designed with a plethora of cabinets & large pantry, The great room has a custom painted accent wall. There's room for an office in part of the living room & storage too. The BR's & laundry room are upstairs. The spacious owners suite has a large walk-in closet. In the ensuite you will find a separate shower, double sinks & a private toilet room. Part of the 3 car garage is now a mud room with many shelves, an A/C unit & epoxy floors. Design your own backyard  The trampoline is ready for jumping. The RV gate is great! Fresh Paint outside.  NOTICE Brand New Community pool, playground, gym, clubhouse with game room ,BBQ area & kiddie pool. Owner will help with Closing Costs! Must see!
